# Weave
**Category:** ventures
**Domain:** healthcare technology / patient communication & practice management
**Website:** https://www.weave.com/

## Overview
Weave is a cloud-based communication and collaboration platform designed for small and medium-sized dental and healthcare practices. It integrates phone systems, text messaging, appointment reminders, online reviews, payment processing, and patient intake forms into a single interface, eliminating the need for multiple disconnected tools. The platform aims to simplify administrative workflows and improve patient engagement by automating routine tasks such as confirmations and follow-ups.

Founded in 2011, Weave has grown rapidly by focusing on the specific operational pain points of independent practices. Its software helps practices reduce no-show rates, gather more online reviews, and streamline billing—areas that directly impact revenue and patient satisfaction. As of 2025, Weave serves tens of thousands of providers across the United States and has expanded its capabilities to include AI‑powered analytics and personalized patient outreach.

## Utah connection
Weave is headquartered in Lehi, Utah, and is a prominent member of the state’s “Silicon Slopes” tech ecosystem. The company benefits from Utah’s strong talent pool in software engineering and customer success, and it has contributed to the region’s reputation as a hub for healthcare technology. Weave’s growth has also drawn attention to Utah as a place where B2B SaaS companies can scale while maintaining a high‑quality workforce. The company went public in 2021 (NYSE: WEAV), further cementing its role as a flagship Utah‑born venture.

